title: Update external documentation on telemetry
body:
### Context

Followup of https://github.com/dotnet/msbuild/issues/10634. Specifically this step:

- [x] Document the datapoints in our wiki
- [ ] Update SDK telemetry docs in [dotnet/docs](https://github.com/dotnet/docs/issues/new?template=z-customer-feedback.yml&pageUrl=https%3A%2F%2Flearn.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fdotnet%2Fcore%2Ftools%2Ftelemetry&pageQueryParams&contentSourceUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fdotnet%2Fdocs%2Fblob%2Fmain%2Fdocs%2Fcore%2Ftools%2Ftelemetry.md&documentVersionIndependentId=50433ae5-4687-fe5f-75ab-a47e1a706777&feedback=%0A%0A%5BEnter+feedback+here%5D%0A&author=%40KathleenDollard&metadata=*+ID%3A+c136055b-bb04-17b6-19b2-42d4610c1a70+%0A*+Service%3A+**dotnet-fundamentals**) - https://github.com/dotnet/docs/issues/43034

As we need to be transparent with our users about telemetry we collect
